 A light broke over the cf. From it came a bright blue
spark. A spark given a second chance for the first was
stolen by a a treachorous spark a spark long since
sent the Pitts where it belonged. The spark took a
body form. The body was a large metal type gorilla.
About 12 feet high. It had a plane mode and a large
robot mode. (A optimal Optimus mode just smaller.) His
eyes blinked online he looked down on the battle. He
sent a private message to his fellow maximals asking
for information on what was happening. He yelled out
into the air. "Look whos back and feelin Prime."
Magnus Prime had returned.
